  {
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Hi there, it's been a while on this issue - wondering if this is on the team's radar still? We can work around some of these by, e.g., wrapping `<Breadcrumb>` in a `<nav aria-label=\"..\">` of our own, but some stuff I have come across that I can't control:\n\n- `<Pagination>` doesn't specify `aria-current=\"page\"`\n- Can't add `aria-label` to `<Hits>` (the `<ol>`, specifically)\n- Using our own button to clear `<SearchBox>` with `useSearchBox` can't be tied to underlying `<input>` with `aria-controls`\n\nI definitely wouldn't say any of these are critical, except perhaps the `aria-current=\"page\"` which is definitely an oversight.",
    "created_at": "2025-03-13T22:45:24Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5188#issuecomment-2722843234",
